{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were selected for it because we were considered being sufficiently tactful and well-educated to be able to do a-- a dirty job, fundamentally a very dirty job, in a-- and in a humane way.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and by-- usually by 4 o'clock in the afternoon, the premises had to be vacated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, we would come in somewhere, typically between say, 7:30 and 11 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always two of us, sometimes three, never one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would notify the inhabitants that your apartment is being confiscated, and you have to move out by 4 o'clock this afternoon.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is the place where you go, and the people will be prepared to receive you because they have been notified.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That was-- that was the task at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That is-- I would say that this started in probably early April and went through May.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then in early June, or late May maybe, the situation changed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that point the ghettoization of Budapest was decided.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, the ghettoization of Budapest was very different from the ghettoization almost anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm not aware of any other city where ghettoization was carried out like in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Ghettos in Poland and Slovakia, and Romania, anywhere else, were closed areas of town, usually surrounded by a wall or by something else, and the Jews live-- and all the Jews live inside the ghetto, and the non-Jews live outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In Budapest, largely because of fear of aerial attacks, the Hungarian authorities-- of course with the approval of the Germans, nothing was done by the Hungarians without the approval of the Germans-- decided to have not a single ghetto surrounded by a wall, but to have ghetto houses.",
      "word_count": 48
    }
  ],
